sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor UserA as RequestSender
actor UserB as RequestReceiver
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant FriendCtrl as FriendController
participant FriendSvc as FriendService
participant FriendDb as MongoFriend
participant Redis as RedisFriendCache
participant Realtime as RealtimeHub
UserA->>Client: Gui loi moi ket ban
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/friends/request
Gateway->>FriendCtrl: sendFriendRequest
FriendCtrl->>FriendSvc: validate self/duplicate
FriendSvc->>FriendDb: save status=pending
FriendSvc->>Redis: invalidate friends:<userA>
FriendSvc->>Realtime: emit friend_request_sent
FriendSvc-->>Client: 201
UserB->>Client: Chap nhan loi moi
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/friends/:friendId/accept
Gateway->>FriendCtrl: acceptFriendRequest
FriendSvc->>FriendDb: update status=accepted
alt Thanh cong
  FriendSvc->>Realtime: emit friend_request_accepted
  FriendSvc-->>Client: 200
else Khong tim thay/khong hop le
  FriendSvc-->>Client: 404/409
end
